    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 62-65.</p><p>Intrepid Attack</p><p>Also at 21st level, you can use a bonus action to gain advantage on your next attack until the end of your turn. If you already have advantage from another source and you use your Intrepid Attack, you can roll an additional d20 as part of the attack and choose the highest from the three dice. While using Intrepid Attack, you cannot have disadvantage on the attack roll by any means.</p></div>",
